{"results":[{"aya":"001","id":5376,"locale":"ja","sura":"070","text":"或る者が，下るべき懲罰に就いて問う。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"002","id":5377,"locale":"ja","sura":"070","text":"不信心者は，それを防ぐことは出来ない。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"003","id":5378,"locale":"ja","sura":"070","text":"階段の主，アッラーから（の懲罰）である。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"004","id":5379,"locale":"ja","sura":"070","text":"天使たちや聖霊（大天使ジブリール）は，一日にして，かれの許に登る，その（一日の）長さは，5万年である。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"005","id":5380,"locale":"ja","sura":"070","text":"だからあなたは，立派に耐え忍べ。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"006","id":5381,"locale":"ja","sura":"070","text":"本当にかれらは，それ（日）を遠いと思う。","translator":"Unknown"},{"aya":"007","id":5382,"locale":"ja","sura":"070","text":"しかしわれは，それを近いと見る。","translator":"Unknown"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":7,"nextPage":"/ja/s070-2.json"}}